Comment: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上阿!!! 艾連!
Comment: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,850年
Comment: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類首次
Comment: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從巨人手中奪回了自己的領土
Comment: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,付出了相當大的犧牲
Comment: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼現在在場的各位
Comment: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們會將你們視為新的調查軍團的一份子來迎接你們
Comment: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是最誠摯的敬禮!
Comment: 0,0:00:36.12,0:00:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,獻出你們的心臟吧!!
Comment: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,虧你們能夠克服內心的恐懼...
Comment: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們是勇敢的士兵
Comment: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我打從心裡尊敬各位
Comment: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一個月後
Comment: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾爾文‧史密斯率領的調查軍團
Comment: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了探索前往可能藏著巨人秘密的希干希納區的路徑
Comment: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從卡拉涅斯區出發了
Comment: 0,0:01:12.22,0:01:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,第57次
Comment: 0,0:01:13.79,0:01:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,牆外調查開始
Comment: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,向前邁進!
Comment: 0,0:01:21.71,0:02:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,左前方10公尺級接近
Comment: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他的肚子裡面有著什麼雖然讓我十分在意...
Comment: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 就交給掩護班了
Comment: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡!
Comment: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太淺了!
Comment: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.38,Default,*,0,0,0,karaoke,快解決他!
Comment: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別亂看了
Comment: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把他交給掩護班 全速前進!
Comment: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前進! 前進!
Comment: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,掩護班的支援到脫離舊市區此為止了
Comment: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這之後 就完全是巨人的領域了
Comment: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們能依靠的只有艾爾文所提出的長距離搜索陣形
Comment: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們特別作戰小組是在這裡
Comment: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,歐魯先生
Comment: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們跟我同期的人能夠打敗巨人吧
Comment: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤 你這傢伙這一個月來都學了些什麼
Comment: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽好了小鬼
Comment: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所謂的牆外調查
Comment: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是避免和巨人交手的戰鬥...
Comment: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,長距離搜索陣形 展開!
Comment: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,先走啦 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算遇到巨人也別慌張啊
Comment: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯 約翰也是
Comment: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,通知前方半圓形區域
Comment: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然距離很長但還是要
Comment: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,確實保持能看到前後左右的距離
Comment: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等距離地散開
Comment: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,盡可能地擴大搜索和傳令範圍
Comment: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒問題的 冷靜點
Comment: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,主要最接近巨人的是前列搜索班的士兵
Comment: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當他一發現巨人就會立刻發射紅色信號彈
Comment: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發現信號彈的士兵會以相同方式傳達下去
Comment: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後得知巨人位置的團長會發射綠色信號彈
Comment: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,決定全體需要變更的路線
Comment: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如此一來整個陣形就能在避開巨人的同時往目的地前進
Comment: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是視線也可能受到障礙物遮蔽以至於較晚發現巨人
Comment: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也可能發生巨人出現在陣形中的情況
Comment: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,紅色 發射紅色信號彈...
Comment: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,布勞斯 這邊
Comment: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡 搜索失誤了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把他引過來
Comment: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,布勞斯! 趁現在往這跑過來
Comment: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剩下由我來 移動囉!
Comment: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是
Comment: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,班長
Comment: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快回位置上
Comment: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙沒力了
Comment: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛才真奇怪 才剛發射紅色煙彈陣形就亂了
Comment: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該不會...
Comment: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然而剛剛這些應對方法都是在容易行動的正常情況下
Comment: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,咦 黑色煙霧彈
Comment: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無視於附近的人類往中央逼近嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,錯不了! 那傢伙是...
Comment: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇行種!
Comment: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有遇到行動無法預測的奇行種才需要戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡 只能硬拼了
Comment: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,希斯 你負責後頸 我來阻止他的行動
Comment: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,了解
Comment: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,立體機動裝置在平地上非常的不利
Comment: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成功率極低
Comment: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但絕不能讓他破壞隊形
Comment: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那邊記得是亞魯雷特吧!
Comment: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還不想讓新兵遇上這傢伙啊...
Comment: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這裡就解決掉!
Comment: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,趁現在 希斯!
Comment: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成功了 尼斯班長
Comment: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成功了嗎？
Comment: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回來啦 不愧是我的愛馬
Comment: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,愛你呀 夏洛特
Comment: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又來了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,右翼搜索班在幹嘛啊!
Comment: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,照這樣看來 那應該也是奇行種
Comment: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真沒辦法
Comment: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,希斯 再來一次
Comment: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是
Comment: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 連續遇上兩次還真夠倒楣
Comment: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且看起來還是14公尺級以上的
Comment: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這傢伙不好對付
Comment: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是怎麼回事 也太快了吧
Comment: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別讓她往亞魯雷特那邊過去! 希斯
Comment: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是
Comment: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 不對
Comment: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不是奇行種
Comment: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙還有智慧
Comment: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟盔甲還有超大型以及艾連一樣
Comment: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是有著巨人身體的人類
Comment: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是誰?
Comment: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼要這麼做？
Comment: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,糟糕了 要怎麼辦？
Comment: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也會死 會被殺掉的
Comment: 0,0:10:58.69,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,去吧 快逃!
Comment: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 這些傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底有什麼目的...
Comment: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰... 誰快去通報一下...
Comment: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,右翼搜索班...
Comment: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幾乎全軍覆沒....
Comment: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女巨人...
Comment: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,帶了一大群的巨人...
Comment: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有沒有誰在啊...
Comment: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她沒殺我?
Comment: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛才那是...?
Comment: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她拉下斗篷...
Comment: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,臉?
Comment: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她在確認我的臉?
Comment: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萊納
Comment: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,站得起來嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 總之 在牆外不騎馬的話根本活不下去
Comment: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快一點!
Comment: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我看到了奇行種的煙霧彈
Comment: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是那個屁股很結實的傢伙嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不是奇行種
Comment: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而是有著巨人身軀的人類!
Comment: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說什麼?!
Comment: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊 等我一下
Comment: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我得先發射煙霧彈才行...
Comment: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快一點...
Comment: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,必須用煙霧彈傳達緊急狀況...
Comment: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等一下
Comment: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰好像已經發射了
Comment: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道是從右翼上來的?
Comment: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,意思是損傷到無法進行作戰的地步嗎...
Comment: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽說右翼搜索班有部分已經遭到擊潰
Comment: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,出現了不少巨人啊
Comment: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然還不清楚狀況如何
Comment: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有好幾個腳程特別快的
Comment: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目前雖然還在拖延他們的行動
Comment: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但已經無法繼續進行偵查任務了
Comment: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且損失相當慘重
Comment: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一不小心就可能會全滅啊
Comment: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是從那傢伙出現的方向來的...
Comment: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道 是那傢伙把巨人給帶過來的?!
Comment: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙?
Comment: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼那裡會出現巨人啊?
Comment: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是奇行種嗎?
Comment: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是...  不一樣的
Comment: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她是有著巨人身軀的人類
Comment: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能夠做出跟艾連相同的事的人類
Comment: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說什麼...?!
Comment: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼你會這樣講?
Comment: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,基本上巨人只會「吃人」
Comment: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而結果就是讓對方死掉
Comment: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「殺人」並非他們的目的
Comment: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但那傢伙在被鎖定要害時
Comment: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將學長們「捏爛」跟「摔死」
Comment: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是為了「吃掉」
Comment: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而是為了「殺人而殺人」
Comment: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這點跟其他巨人在本質上是不同的
Comment: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當初超大型跟盔甲型巨人破壞城牆時
Comment: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將大批巨人帶進來的也一定是她
Comment: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目的很明顯就是要攻擊人類
Comment: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不... 該怎麼說...
Comment: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我覺得她好像在找誰
Comment: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果沒猜錯的話...
Comment: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼在找的人就是...
Comment: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道是... 艾連?!
Comment: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說艾連?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.13,Default,Q,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連所在的里維班
Comment: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該就是負責當時她出現的右翼啊
Comment: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,右翼?
Comment: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是交到我手上的作戰企劃書上寫的卻是在左翼後方欸
Comment: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我那份上寫的是在右翼前方
Comment: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對... 應該不可能配置在前線才對
Comment: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那他到底會在哪裡?
Comment: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該是在陣形中最安全的地方
Comment: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是這樣的話
Comment: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該是在中央偏後吧...
Comment: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在沒閒時間想那個了
Comment: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙的行為是不可能用煙霧彈來傳達的
Comment: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這期間 連指揮班也會被殲滅掉
Comment: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是整個陣形都會瓦解然後全滅的
Comment: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你到底想說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說
Comment: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個距離應該還能吸引到她的注意
Comment: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說不定我們可以爭取到更多的撤退時間...
Comment: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,的意思...
Comment: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙真的具有智慧
Comment: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以她的角度來看我們就像是蟲子一樣
Comment: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,隨便一踩就爛了喔!
Comment: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的假的啊...
Comment: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那樣就太恐怖了...
Comment: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你真的是約翰嗎...
Comment: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我認識的約翰應該是只會為自己著想的人欸
Comment: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這麼說也太失禮了吧...
Comment: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只是...
Comment: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不想讓那個已經成為根本分不清誰是誰的骨灰失望罷了...
Comment: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我啊...
Comment: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我很清楚自己現在應該做些什麼!
Comment: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且 這可是我們自己選擇的工作!
Comment: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們也把力量借給我啊!
Comment: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把帽子戴上 壓低一點!
Comment: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要讓她看到你的臉!
Comment: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙在還沒分清誰是誰之前
Comment: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該不會輕易動手的
Comment: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原來如此
Comment: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她不會殺死有可能是艾連的人
Comment: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:26.76,Default,*,0,0,0,karaoke,不需要擔心她的視力正合我意
Comment: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,順便期待看她是不是真的眼睛不好吧
Comment: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然你之前老是跟艾連黏在一起讓我覺得很噁心
Comment: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過其實你還蠻能幹的
Comment: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喔... 謝謝...
Comment: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過你說噁心還真過分...
Comment: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟剛才比起來速度減緩了許多...
Comment: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然是累了嗎...
Comment: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果再讓她以當時的速度狂奔就來不及了
Comment: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該立刻動手
Comment: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,必須在現在動手!
Comment: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們給我聽好了
Comment: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就跟剛才說的一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,盡量吸引她的注意
Comment: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓整個陣形可以撤退
Comment: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,盡可能要把她困在這裡
Comment: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果可以削掉她的腳根當然是最好的
Comment: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是你們千萬別逞強啊
Comment: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可不能被解決掉啊
Comment: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,弱點應該一樣都在後頸上
Comment: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她跟其他的巨人截然不同
Comment: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要收拾掉應該是不可能的吧
Comment: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,至少... 就人類的常識來看應該是這樣子...
Comment: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但若是他們兩個的話 說不定...
Comment: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏!
Comment: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,行動的精確度遠超過其他巨人啊!
Comment: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡!
Comment: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太小看...
Comment: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太小看她了!
Comment: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然知道要保護後頸!
Comment: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰!
Comment: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡!
Comment: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經逃不掉了!
Comment: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要死了 鋼索被抓到就一切都結束了
Comment: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,約翰!
Comment: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,替那個趕著去投胎的傢伙報仇吧!
Comment: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏?
Comment: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,停住不動了?!
Comment: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是她! 就是被她殺死的!
Comment: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,右翼的那傢伙在趕著去投胎的路上就掛了
Comment: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,替那個趕著去投胎的傢伙報仇吧!
Comment: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生什麼事了
Comment: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他是撞到腦袋錯亂了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,麻煩了 偏偏在這時候
Comment: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萊納?
Comment: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我最好的朋友就是被這傢伙踩死的!
Comment: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我當時看到他就黏在她的腳下!
Comment: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他想直接攻擊後頸嗎?!
Comment: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不! 會成功!
Comment: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是她的目光被阿爾敏吸引過去的現在的話!
Comment: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂...
Comment: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萊納... 你...
Comment: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,萊納這傢伙竟然真的動手了...
Comment: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎的表現太過顯眼讓我都忘了
Comment: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,其實他也是個出類拔萃又優秀的傢伙啊
Comment: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爭取到的時間應該夠多了吧
Comment: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點遠離這個傢伙!
Comment: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果她不會吃人的話
Comment: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼應該是不會追上來的!
Comment: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看吧!
Comment: 0,0:22:03.98,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個高大的女人
Comment: 0,0:22:05.73,0:22:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被我們嚇到打算落跑回家了!
Comment: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不會吧...
Comment: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那邊是中央後方...
Comment: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該不會是艾連所在的位置...
Comment: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個怪物...
Comment: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,連訓練有素的調查兵
Comment: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,都無法阻止的女巨人...
Comment: 0,0:24:01.24,0:24:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然而這怪物在有著巨樹的森林裡
Comment: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,終於找到了艾連的身影...
